    "description": "以培養學生能以創新觀點,撰寫創意、創業企畫為主。課程內容將包括：創業企劃介紹、市場評估調查、行銷模組、財務規劃、營運規劃等重要議題。並於期末完成模擬企劃書。",
    "prerequisites": "",
    "syllabus": {
        "zh": "1.課程介紹及分組<br>2.商務企劃實例介紹分析<br>3.撰寫商務企劃書前的準備<br>4.如何撰寫商務企劃書<br>5.各組訂立企劃主題並發表<br>6.各組市場分析及行銷規劃<br>7.各組發表財務規劃及營運計劃<br>8.各組商務企劃簡報<br>9.繳交商務企劃書<br>",
        "en": "1.\tCourse introduction and grouping<br>2.\tIntroduction to business planning examples<br>3.\tPreparation before writing a business plan<br>4.\tHow to write a business plan<br>5.\tEach group has a planning theme and published<br>6.\tGroup analysis and marketing planning<br>7.\tEach group publishes financial planning and operating plans<br>8.\tBusiness planning briefings of each group<br>9.\tSubmit a business plan<br>"
